# PhotoEdit C++ formatting. Authoritative; do not hand-format against this.
# Based on Google style with project overrides (see docs/04-coding-standards.md).
---
Language: Cpp
BasedOnStyle: Google
Standard: c++20
IndentWidth: 4
ColumnLimit: 100
PointerAlignment: Left
DerivePointerAlignment: false
AccessModifierOffset: -4
AllowShortFunctionsOnASingleLine: Inline
AllowShortIfStatementsOnASingleLine: WithoutElse
IncludeBlocks: Preserve
SortIncludes: CaseSensitive
...
